nodes.text: TK-9091 was the designation of a human male Stormtrooper Commander who served in Darth Vader's personal stormtrooper legion, Vader's Fist. During the secret mission to Tatooine, TK-9091 was killed by Princess Leia Organa aboard the Tantive IV.
TK-9091 appears in the 1977 film Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. He was later identified in the short story "The Bucket" from the 2017 anthology book From a Certain Point of View.

In the 2016 graphic novel Star Wars: The Original Trilogy – A Graphic Novel, TK-9091 survives his confrontation with Leia Organa aboard the Tantive IV. There, Organa shoots a stun blast which TK-9091 dodges and hits another stormtrooper instead, leading TK-9091 to stun Organa.
